Class HelpMojo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
      • com.soebes.maven.plugins.dmg.HelpMojo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.maven.plugin.ContextEnabled, org.apache.maven.plugin.Mojo

    public class HelpMojo
extends org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
    Display help information on doxygen-maven-plugin.
    Call 
      mvn doxygen:help -Ddetail=true -Dgoal=<goal-name>
    to display parameter details.
    Version:
    generated on Sat Sep 14 15:02:29 CEST 2013
    Author:
    org.apache.maven.tools.plugin.generator.PluginHelpGenerator (version 2.5.1)

        Parameters:
        text - The text to split into lines, must not be null.
        indent - The base indentation level of each line, must not be negative.
